title: Grindmaster Dead - Stronger Than Love (1994)
description:
Grindmaster Dead was a doom/death metal band with folk elements from Riga, Latvia. They persisted from 1991 - 1995 when they changed their name to Skyforger, which is well-known Latvian folk/pagan metal band now.

This is their only full-length release (but there exists some other releases and unreleased demo tapes).

* Grindmaster Dead - Stronger Than Love (1994)

1. The Tree Ravens (2:00)
2. Stronger Than Love (7:08)
3. At The Wizard's Sabbath (4:38)
4. Summer Gods (3:29)
5. This Realm of Silence (2:16)
6. Under The Willow Tree (7:30)
